           <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:60px;">
        <h2 style="color:#3453a5; margin-top: -30px; margin-bottom: 0; padding: 0;" class="main_title"> NON-DESTRUCTIVE TESTING SOCIETY(SINGAPORE)</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0; padding: 0;width: 100%; text-align: center;">SGNDT Number: <span style="color: #1712fd; padding-top: 10px;">' . $certificate_number . ' Issue 0</span></p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0; padding: 0;margin-top: 15px;">This is to certify that</p>
        <h3 style="color: #0001fc; margin-top: 0; padding-top: 5px; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600;">' . strtoupper($entry['1']) . '</h3>
